@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home Page";
}

<div class="jumbotron text-center">
    <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to the Todo App</h1>
    <p class="lead">Organize your tasks effectively with the Quadrant system!</p>
    <hr class="my-4">
    <br /><br />
    <p>Learn how to prioritize tasks using the Quadrant system inspired by "The 7 Habits of Highly Effective People" by Steven Covey.</p>
    <p class="lead">
        <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="https://www.amazon.com/Habits-Highly-Effective-People/dp/1471195201/ref=asc_df_1471195201&mcid=30b2c55462e5342ca8e1bde41ad7adf5?tag=bingshoppinga-20&linkCode=df0&hvadid=80127029710338&hvnetw=o&hvqmt=e&hvbmt=be&hvdev=c&hvlocint=&hvlocphy=&hvtargid=pla-4583726554854239&psc=1" role="button">Purchase Book</a>
    </p>
</div>
<br /><br /><br />
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>What is the Quadrant System?</h2>
        <p>Discover how Quadrants I, II, III, and IV can help you categorize and prioritize your tasks based on importance and urgency.</p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-secondary" href="https://timeular.com/blog/time-management-matrix/" role="button">Learn More &raquo;</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>Add/Edit Tasks</h2>
        <p>Create, update, and manage your tasks with ease. Use the Add/Edit Task feature to keep your to-do list organized.</p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-secondary" asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="CreateTask">Start Adding Tasks &raquo;</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>View Quadrants</h2>
        <p>Visualize your tasks in Quadrants and easily identify what needs your immediate attention or can be scheduled for later.</p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-secondary" asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Quadrants">Explore Quadrants &raquo;</a></p>
    </div>
</div>
